Usage: reset_driving_cell [-help] <port_list> [-fall] [-max] [-min] [-rise]

-help           # Prints out the command usage
<port_list>     # List of ports (string, required)
-fall           # Resets the falling drive assertion (bool, optional)
-max            # Resets the late drive assertion (bool, optional)
-min            # Resets the early drive assertion (bool, optional)
-rise           # Resets the rising drive assertion (bool, optional)